  "repo_truth": "Two fresh HCM-0.8 reviews returned Required findings. The active parent remediated both rounds, including historical-admission fixture isolation, schema-authoritative dispatch examples, ordered meta-skill enforcement, and final-vs-historical subject-manifest validation. This manifest binds the complete current dirty documentation/control-plane subject; no Rust paths are included.",
