    "Read every path in subject_manifest and both prior HCM-0.8 immutable review dispatches.",
    "Run read-only schema, semantic-lineage, manifest-replay, history-admission, ledger, link, portability, archive, docs-only, and whitespace checks.",
    "Return findings only; do not edit, commit, create a handoff, append the ledger, or create another dispatch."
  ],
  "non_goals": [
    "No Rust or runtime implementation.",
    "No edits to immutable records or dispatches.",
    "No reuse of either prior reviewer or their conclusions as authority.",
    "No global handoff, ledger write, or user task hop by the reviewer."
  ],
  "tasks": [
    "Independently review the complete twice-remediated subject without relying on the parent success claim.",
    "Retest every Required finding from both prior reviews, including admission-fixture isolation, schema/example agreement, using-agent-skills ordering, stop/status/resume admission, typed remediation lineage, and final-versus-historical manifest behavior.",
    "Verify one active parent still owns HCM-0.8 and all coupled documents, schemas, templates, and validator behavior agree.",
    "Replay this subject manifest against live files before review, run the full proof wall, and return findings first with severity, file/line, violated contract/gate, smallest remediation, and missing proof."
  ],
